	office:  (217) 244-0070
</dl>



<H2> Research Project: </H2>

	As part of my thesis work I designed and developed 
	<!WA7><A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~snovack//~snovack/overview/project_description.html">EVE,
	a retargetable,
	parallelizing compiler for fine-grain parallel architectures</A>.
	My general research interests include parallel algorithms and
	architectures, parallelizing compilers, and hardware/software
	codesign.
<P>
